Metadata: Currents Sea Grant Newsletter (August, September, and December 1973; First issues/No volume number)
Oregon State University Sea Grant Program
Three newsletter issues in one entry for 1973.

The following cover articles are in these newsletter issues for 1973: August: Whiter, brighter Surveys show seafoods safe; National SG Meeting set for October 8-10, 1973. September: Fewer Fish; More Fishermen: Tragedy?; Ken :Hilderbrand selected as new MAP leader. December: What Happened to the Dungeness?
